profile:
We are specialized in the production of fine kitchen cabinets, custom shelving, and high-end closet storage solutions . We are confident in the products we make, as well as the services we provide, on every project will suit your vision.

20 years of experience
Our 20 years of experience led to remodeling any kitchen, wall unit, home office, or walk-in closet style you like

Whether meeting with you and your family or collaborating with architects, contractors, and interior decorators, we’re here to help you define your scope of work and articulate a vision that’s uniquely yours.


The experienced design team will turn your vision into a reality detailed plan, creating custom solutions that blend form a function to fit all your family’s needs.

Build
Our designs of combining the old and the new world approach to the top of craftsmanship and that mean you can have the best rich design from both worlds for kitchens or bathrooms. We make every piece of cabinetry in our shop in Toronto, Proudly 100% Canadian-made. To this regard, we offer a warranty against defects in materials and/or workmanship for a period of two years under average residential usage.  

Our Values
We believe in building durable and functional cabinetry that will make things easy to store, easy to find, and easy to clean. By choosing to work with us you will get the real value for your investment and your cabinets will look as good up close as they do from a distance.
name: Wildwood Kitchens

profile:
The Home Organizers specialize in design and organizational services.  With more than 60 years of combined experience, we are uniquely qualified to carry out design, manufacture and installation for our clients, and we use a number of advanced tools to deliver gorgeous results. Custom Products for your: Kitchens, Closets, Vanities, Mud Rooms, Home Offices, Custom Cabinetry, Accessories, Wardrobes, Wall and Entertainment Units. 

***

Our services include:

A Thorough In-Home Consultation
On-Site Measurements and Analysis
3D-Rendered Designs for an Early Look at Your Completed Projects
Manufacturing for Cabinetry and Other Custom Pieces
Full Delivery and Installation
And More…

*****

Our goal is to leave you with a gorgeous, organized and functional home, and we’re ready to show you the advantages of working with an experienced team of designers, manufacturers and installers. Book Your FREE In-Home Consultation.

profile: Welcome to IQ Closets. Making visions your reality since 2005! Are your closest so poorly designed and you're not able to access your full closet space? We have solutions to solve your problems. We specialize in Custom Closets and Custom Wall Units and offer free onsite consultations and appointments in our showroom. We can come to your home or you're welcome to come see us in our showroom. In addition to custom closets we provide construction services such as changing your single closet door into a double door to maximize your closet space. Contact us today to schedule your appointment.
